quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,16,"Ɓen wi'ooɓe: \"Joomi amen, menen men gomɗinii, yawtan men junubaaji amen, daɗndaa men lepte yiite"
  3,17,Muññiiɓe ɓen e goonguɓe ɓen e ɗoftiiɓe ɓen e wiŋtooɓe=nafkoobe ɓen e insinotooɓe ɓen ka hoore-subaka
  3,18,"Alla Seedike wonde Reweteeɗo alaa si wanaa kaŋko, Malaa'ika en kadi, e joomiraaɓe ganndal ɓen, ko O Daraniiɗo nunɗal. Reweteeɗo alaa si wanaa Kaŋko, On Fooluɗo Ñeeñuɗo"
  3,19,"Pellet diina kan ka Alla, ko lislaamu. Okkaaɓe Defte ɓen lurraali si wanaa ɓaawo nde ganndal ngal arde ɓe; ka bewre hakkunde maɓɓe. Kala yedduɗo aayeeje Alla ɗen, pellet Alla ko yaawuɗo hasboore"
  3,20,"Si ɓe wennjii ma, maaku: \"Mi jebbilanii yeeso an ngon e on jokkuɗo lam\". Maakanaa ɓen okkaaɓe Defte e humambinne en: \" E on jebbilike?\" Si ɓe jebbilike, gomɗii ɓe feewii, si ɓe huccitii, enee, ko fawi maa ko yottingol. Alla ko Reŋtuɗo jeyaaɓe ɓen"
  3,21,"Pellet, ɓen yeddooɓe aayeeje Alla ɗen, ɓe wara Annabaaɓe ɓen ko aldaa e goonga, ɓe wara ɓen yamirooɓe nunɗal, wewlinir ɓe lepte muusuɗe"
  3,22,"Ko ɓen woni ɓe golleeji mun boni ɓen ka aduna e ka laakara, ɓe alaa wallooɓe"